data.title: High Knees
instruction: Stand straight with feet hip-width apart
Lift your knees to your chest while jogging in place
Keep your back straight and core engaged
Pump your arms to maintain balance and rhythm
Repeat for the set duration

data.title: Butt Kicks
instruction: Stand straight with feet shoulder-width apart
Jog in place while kicking your heels up to touch your glutes
Keep your arms bent and swing them naturally
Maintain a steady pace throughout the movement
Repeat for the set duration

data.title: Jogging in Place
instruction: Stand tall with feet hip-width apart
Begin jogging in place with light, quick steps
Keep your shoulders relaxed and swing your arms naturally
Focus on warming up your legs and increasing your heart rate
Repeat for the set duration

data.title: Side Lunges
instruction: Stand tall with feet hip-width apart and hands at your chest or hips.
Take a big step to the right, shifting your weight onto your right leg.
Bend your right knee while keeping your left leg straight and your back flat.
Push your hips back and lower until your right thigh is parallel to the floor.
Push off your right foot to return to the starting position.
Alternate sides and repeat for the desired duration or repetitions.
